### Enhancements

* Cache the expanded search path inside `Configuration._set_search_path()` so repeated calls with the same arguments (e.g. successive `reset_context()` invocations) skip the filesystem stat and directory-iteration work. `raw_data` is still reloaded on every call, so condarc changes are picked up normally. The expanded search path is now stored as a `tuple` instead of a lazy generator. (#15867)

